<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2360064.How_Not_to_Write_a_Novel"><img alt="How Not to Write a Novel: 200 Classic Mistakes and How to Avoid Them—A Misstep-by-Misstep Guide" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1332803117l/2360064._SX98_.jpg" />
